---
import SidebarLayout from '../../../layouts/SidebarLayout.astro';
import "../../../styles/global.css";
---

<SidebarLayout app="c">
  <h1 class="text-xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-5 text-custom-accent text-center">
    Loops in C
  </h1>

  <section class="mb-5 space-y-6 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-custom-secondary">
    <p>
      Loops are used to execute a block of code repeatedly. C provides three types of loops: for, while, and do-while.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-custom-accent mt-6 mb-3">For Loop</h2>

    <div class="bg-custom-secondary border border-custom rounded-lg p-3 sm:p-4 my-4">
      <pre class="text-xs sm:text-sm overflow-x-auto whitespace-pre-wrap"><code>{`#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
    // Print numbers from 1 to 5
    for (int i = 1; i <= 5; i++) {
        printf("%d ", i);
    }
    printf("\\n");
    
    return 0;
}`}</code></pre>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-custom-accent mt-6 mb-3">While Loop</h2>

    <div class="bg-custom-secondary border border-custom rounded-lg p-3 sm:p-4 my-4">
      <pre class="text-xs sm:text-sm overflow-x-auto whitespace-pre-wrap"><code>{`#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
    int count = 1;
    
    // Print numbers from 1 to 5
    while (count <= 5) {
        printf("%d ", count);
        count++;
    }
    printf("\\n");
    
    return 0;
}`}</code></pre>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-custom-secondary border border-custom rounded-2xl p-4 sm:p-6 mt-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-custom-accent mb-3">Loop Comparison</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 pl-4">
        <li><strong class="text-custom-primary">For loop</strong>: Used when number of iterations is known</li>
        <li><strong class="text-custom-primary">While loop</strong>: Used when number of iterations is unknown</li>
        <li><strong class="text-custom-primary">Do-while loop</strong>: Executes at least once, then checks condition</li>
        <li>Use <code class="bg-custom-primary text-custom-secondary px-1 rounded text-sm">break</code> to exit loop immediately</li>
        <li>Use <code class="bg-custom-primary text-custom-secondary px-1 rounded text-sm">continue</code> to skip current iteration</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</SidebarLayout>